summary: “I Love His Eyes: David Tennant” - Digital Oil Painting  A little while ago someone sent me an ask for artist advice. One of the...
caption:
“I Love His Eyes: David Tennant” - Digital Oil Painting

A little while ago someone sent me an ask for artist advice. One of the things I said was to draw the same things over and over and it occurred to me that I usually don’t post the ‘practice’ stuff that I do. (Mostly because it looks like this.) But I thought showing you guys the ‘process’ I do might be helpful, so here are four different versions of DT’s eyes, I tried to capture a different expression each time, so they are the same but different.
